Label: Product classification type name
Description: A name which identifies a proprietary classification scheme (ie a scheme which is not a standard and for which there is no individual scheme type code). Should be included when, and only when, the code in the <ProductClassificationType> element indicates a proprietary scheme, ie the sender’s own category scheme. Optional and non-repeating.
Format: <dd>Variable length text, suggested maximum length 50 characters</dd>
